---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About RemoteWorkHQ"
  description="RemoteWorkHQ helps remote workers build productive, comfortable home offices with free tools, honest gear reviews, and practical guides."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">About RemoteWorkHQ</h1>
        <div class="mt-10 prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
          <p>
            Remote work is not going away. In 2026, over 60% of employed Americans work remotely at least part-time. But most people were thrown into working from home without any guidance on how to set up a proper workspace. They work from kitchen tables, couches, and makeshift desks — and their bodies and productivity pay the price.
          </p>
          <p>
            We built RemoteWorkHQ to fix that. Our mission is to help every remote worker build a home office that is comfortable, productive, and fits their space and budget. No interior design degree required.
          </p>

          <h2>What We Do</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Free Interactive Tools</strong> — Plan your home office layout, calculate ergonomic measurements, find remote jobs, and assess your productivity. All tools run in your browser — no data is ever collected.</li>
            <li><strong>Honest Buying Guides</strong> — We research and compare home office gear across every budget. We are not sponsored by brands. Our recommendations are based on real user reviews, expert opinions, and hands-on testing where possible.</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Setup Guides</strong> — Step-by-step instructions for every aspect of your home office, from desk selection to cable management to lighting. Written in plain English, not designer jargon.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
          <p>
            RemoteWorkHQ is free to use. We make money through advertising (Google AdSense). When you click on an ad, we earn a small commission at no cost to you. Some of our gear recommendations include affiliate links — if you buy through those links, we may earn a commission. This never affects our recommendations; we only recommend products we genuinely believe are the best fit.
          </p>

          <h2>Our Approach</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>No fluff.</strong> Every article gets straight to the point with actionable advice.</li>
            <li><strong>Every budget matters.</strong> We cover gear from $30 to $3,000. Not everyone can afford a $1,500 chair, and that is okay.</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy first.</strong> Our tools run entirely in your browser. No accounts, no data collection, no creepy tracking.</li>
            <li><strong>Science-backed.</strong> Ergonomic recommendations are based on published research and industry standards (OSHA, ANSI/BIFMA).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
